metadata.name: Bubblegum Dreams
metadata.description: "In the realm of bubblegum dreams, we are free to let our imaginations run wild and embrace the boundless potential of youth. For it is in the pursuit of these fanciful thoughts that we find the courage to take risks and discover new paths. So let us all pop a piece of bubblegum, close our eyes, and let our bubblegum dreams carry us towards a brighter tomorrow."
